long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: OmniParser is a cutting-edge SaaS AI tool that intelligently parses UI screenshots into structured data. Powered by advanced Microsoft AI models, it combines YOLOv8 and BLIP-2 technologies to enhance UI automation, testing, and analysis. Perfect for developers, designers, and automation specialists.
